{
  "stem": "4710.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after a few days, they-- they set up a kitchen, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not especially for the camp, because not many people there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But also we were free to roam around in there, from the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we went, we left the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went to the-- wherever you can get food, begging from the peasants and religious.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We're not going to stay here, especially myself and other boys my age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a-- two grown up people who were adopted us for selfish reason.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because they-- like that, if with two children and two adults, you could-- you could-- you could get more-- when it comes to begging, it's easier.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we done it for a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and this is not a-- to go around begging.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we found that there is in Sosnowiec, there's a Red Cross who is going to deal with survivors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went-- we went to Sosnowiec, also few kilometers from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a-- for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember we had some bread, and all-- all the time we had cooked dried peas, nothing else, just peas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I think I had enough by then from the peas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I thought I will go further to-- the I went to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother stayed in that hospital camp, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't come on the same, march, he did not come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was liberated there and then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because contrary to expectations, they didn't manage to evacuate the hospital camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the hospital camp-- hospital camp liberated intact, except those who died in the hospital camp for natural reasons.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Althamer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Althamer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, I-- I don't know anybody from that camp, so I didn't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Possibly historians may know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
